Package: nautilus-add-to-desktop
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-nautilus, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0
Maintainer: morjaradat <your-email@example.com>
Description: Add files and folders to desktop via context menu
 This Nautilus extension adds a "Add to Desktop" option to the
 right-click context menu, allowing users to quickly create
 symbolic links to files and folders on their desktop.
 .
 Features:
  - Right-click context menu integration
  - Automatic name conflict handling
  - Undo functionality
  - Desktop notifications
